snippet.title: GRILLED CHICKEN WINGS | Juicy BBQ Chicken Wings Grilled in Village | Smoky Charcoal Chicken Recipe
snippet.description:
In this video, we prepare delicious grilled chicken wings using a traditional charcoal firewood grill in our village. The chicken wings are marinated with a homemade blend of spices, curd, and a hint of lemon for that perfect tang. Cooked slowly over glowing embers, every bite is juicy, smoky, and full of authentic BBQ flavor.

Watch as we roast the wings to golden perfection on skewers, turning them gently to prevent burning and retain moisture. The smoky aroma, the natural outdoor cooking, and the crispy edges come together to make this one of the best chicken recipes we'll ever try.

pl.title: GRILLOWANE SKRZYDEŁKA Z KURCZAKA | Soczyste skrzydełka z kurczaka BBQ grillowane w Village | Prze...
pl.description:
W tym filmie przygotowujemy pyszne grillowane skrzydełka kurczaka, używając tradycyjnego grilla węglowego opalanego drewnem w naszej wiosce. Skrzydełka kurczaka są marynowane w domowej mieszance przypraw, twarogu i odrobinie cytryny, aby uzyskać idealny smak. Powoli pieczone nad żarzącymi się węglami, każdy kęs jest soczysty, wędzony i pełen autentycznego smaku BBQ.

Zobacz, jak pieczemy skrzydełka do złotej perfekcji na szaszłykach, delikatnie je obracając, aby zapobiec przypaleniu i zachować wilgoć. Wędzony aromat, naturalne gotowanie na świeżym powietrzu i chrupiące brzegi łączą się, aby stworzyć jeden z najlepszych przepisów na kurczaka, jaki kiedykolwiek wypróbujemy.

fr-FR.title: AILES DE POULET GRILLÉES | Ailes de poulet juteuses grillées au barbecue | Recette de poulet fumé...
fr-FR.description:
Dans cette vidéo, nous préparons de délicieuses ailes de poulet grillées sur un gril traditionnel au charbon de bois de notre village. Les ailes sont marinées avec un mélange maison d'épices, du lait caillé et une touche de citron pour une acidité parfaite. Cuites lentement sur des braises incandescentes, chaque bouchée est juteuse, fumée et regorge d'une authentique saveur barbecue.

Regardez-nous rôtir les ailes jusqu'à ce qu'elles soient dorées à la perfection sur des brochettes, en les retournant délicatement pour éviter qu'elles ne brûlent et conserver leur moelleux. L'arôme fumé, la cuisson naturelle en plein air et le croustillant des bords s'associent pour faire de cette recette de poulet l'une des meilleures que nous ayons jamais goûtées.

ko.title: 구운 치킨 윙 | 마을에서 구운 육즙 가득한 바비큐 치킨 윙 | 스모키 숯불 치킨 레시피
ko.description:
이 영상에서는 저희 마을의 전통 숯불 장작 그릴을 이용해 맛있는 구운 닭 날개를 만드는 과정을 보여드립니다. 닭 날개는 수제 향신료와 커드, 그리고 완벽한 새콤함을 위해 레몬 향을 살짝 더해 재워둡니다. 활활 타오르는 숯불 위에서 천천히 구워내 한 입 한 입마다 육즙과 스모키한 풍미, 그리고 정통 바비큐 풍미가 가득합니다.

꼬치에 꽂아 황금빛으로 완벽하게 구워지는 닭 날개를 천천히 돌려가며 타지 않고 수분을 유지하는 과정을 지켜보세요. 훈제 향, 자연스러운 야외 조리, 그리고 바삭한 가장자리가 어우러져 저희가 평생 먹어본 최고의 치킨 레시피 중 하나가 탄생했습니다.

nl-NL.title: GEGRILDE KIPPENVLEUGELS | Sappige BBQ-kippenvleugels gegrild in Village | Recept voor gerookte ho...
nl-NL.description:
In deze video bereiden we heerlijke gegrilde kippenvleugels op een traditionele houtskoolgrill in ons dorp. De kippenvleugels worden gemarineerd met een zelfgemaakte mix van kruiden, wrongel en een vleugje citroen voor die perfecte pittigheid. Langzaam gegaard boven gloeiende kolen, is elke hap sappig, rokerig en vol authentieke BBQ-smaak.

Zie hoe we de vleugels goudbruin roosteren aan spiesjes, waarbij we ze voorzichtig omdraaien om aanbranden te voorkomen en de sappigheid te behouden. De rokerige geur, het natuurlijke buitengaren en de knapperige randjes zorgen er samen voor dat dit een van de beste kiprecepten is die we ooit zullen proberen.

es-US.title: ALITAS DE POLLO A LA PLANCHA | Jugosas alitas de pollo BBQ a la parrilla en el pueblo | Receta de...
es-US.description:
En este video, preparamos deliciosas alitas de pollo a la parrilla en una parrilla de carbón tradicional de nuestro pueblo. Las alitas se marinan con una mezcla casera de especias, requesón y un toque de limón para lograr ese toque ácido perfecto. Cocinadas lentamente sobre brasas, cada bocado es jugoso, ahumado y lleno del auténtico sabor a barbacoa.

Mira cómo asamos las alitas hasta que quedan perfectamente doradas en brochetas, dándoles la vuelta con cuidado para evitar que se quemen y conservar la humedad. El aroma ahumado, la cocción natural al aire libre y los bordes crujientes se combinan para hacer de esta una de las mejores recetas de pollo que jamás hayamos probado.

hi.title: ग्रिल्ड चिकन विंग्स | रसदार BBQ चिकन विंग्स गांव में ग्रिल्ड | स्मोकी चारकोल चिकन रेसिपी
hi.description:
इस वीडियो में, हम अपने गांव में पारंपरिक चारकोल फायरवुड ग्रिल का उपयोग करके स्वादिष्ट ग्रिल्ड चिकन विंग्स तैयार करते हैं। चिकन विंग्स को मसालों, दही और नींबू के एक संकेत के साथ घर के बने मिश्रण के साथ मैरीनेट किया जाता है ताकि वह सही स्वाद ले सके। धीरे-धीरे जलते अंगारों पर पकाए जाने पर, हर निवाला रसदार, धुएँदार और प्रामाणिक BBQ स्वाद से भरा होता है।

देखिए कि हम पंखों को सुनहरा होने तक कैसे भूनते हैं, उन्हें जलने से बचाने और नमी बनाए रखने के लिए उन्हें धीरे-धीरे घुमाते हैं। धुएँदार सुगंध, प्राकृतिक आउटडोर खाना पकाने और कुरकुरे किनारे मिलकर इसे सबसे अच्छी चिकन रेसिपी में से एक बनाते हैं जिसे हम कभी भी आजमाएँगे।

de-DE.title: GEGRILLTE HÜHNCHENFLÜGEL | Saftige BBQ-Hähnchenflügel im Dorf gegrillt | Rezept für rauchiges Häh...
de-DE.description:
In diesem Video bereiten wir köstliche gegrillte Hähnchenflügel auf einem traditionellen Holzkohlegrill in unserem Dorf zu. Die Hähnchenflügel werden mit einer hausgemachten Gewürzmischung, Quark und einem Hauch Zitrone für den perfekten Geschmack mariniert. Langsam über glühender Glut gegart, ist jeder Bissen saftig, rauchig und voller authentischem BBQ-Geschmack.

Sehen Sie zu, wie wir die Flügel auf Spießen goldbraun braten und dabei vorsichtig wenden, um ein Anbrennen zu verhindern und die Feuchtigkeit zu erhalten. Das rauchige Aroma, das natürliche Garen im Freien und die knusprigen Ränder machen dieses Rezept zu einem der besten Hähnchenrezepte, die wir je probiert haben.

ja.title: グリルチキンウィング | 村で焼くジューシーなBBQチキンウィング | スモーキーな炭火焼きチキンのレシピ
ja.description:
この動画では、村の伝統的な炭火焼きグリルを使って、美味しいグリルチキンウィングを作ります。チキンウィングは、自家製のスパイス、カード、そしてほんのりとしたレモンの風味をブレンドしたマリネ液に漬け込み、完璧な酸味を引き出しています。燃え盛る炭火でじっくりと焼き上げるチキンウィングは、一口ごとにジューシーでスモーキー、そして本格的なバーベキューの風味が広がります。

串に刺したチキンウィングを、焦げ付かないように優しくひっくり返し、黄金色になるまで焼き上げる様子をご覧ください。スモーキーな香り、自然なアウトドア調理、そしてカリカリの端が絶妙に調和し、これまで食べたチキンレシピの中でも最高の一品となっています。

id.title: SAYAP AYAM PANGGANG | Sayap Ayam Panggang Lezat di Desa | Resep Ayam Panggang Arang Asap
id.description:
Dalam video ini, kami menyiapkan sayap ayam panggang yang lezat menggunakan panggangan arang kayu bakar tradisional di desa kami. Sayap ayam direndam dengan campuran rempah-rempah, dadih, dan sedikit lemon buatan sendiri untuk rasa asam yang sempurna. Dimasak perlahan di atas bara api yang menyala, setiap gigitannya berair, berasap, dan penuh dengan cita rasa BBQ yang autentik.

Saksikan saat kami memanggang sayap hingga keemasan sempurna di tusuk sate, membaliknya dengan lembut agar tidak gosong dan mempertahankan kelembapan. Aroma berasap, masakan alami di luar ruangan, dan tepian yang renyah berpadu menjadikan ini salah satu resep ayam terbaik yang pernah kami coba.

it.title: ALI DI POLLO ALLA GRIGLIA | Ali di pollo succose al barbecue grigliate nel villaggio | Ricetta de...
it.description:
In questo video, prepariamo deliziose alette di pollo alla griglia utilizzando una tradizionale griglia a legna del nostro villaggio. Le alette di pollo sono marinate con una miscela fatta in casa di spezie, cagliata e un pizzico di limone per un sapore acidulo perfetto. Cotte lentamente sulla brace, ogni boccone è succoso, affumicato e ricco di autentico sapore barbecue.

Guardate come arrostiamo le alette fino a doratura perfetta su spiedini, girandole delicatamente per evitare che si brucino e mantenere l'umidità. L'aroma affumicato, la cottura naturale all'aperto e i bordi croccanti si uniscono per rendere questa una delle migliori ricette di pollo che proveremo mai.

pt-BR.title: ASAS DE FRANGO GRELHADAS | Asas de Frango Suculentas Grelhadas na Vila | Receita de Frango Defuma...
pt-BR.description:
Neste vídeo, preparamos deliciosas asas de frango grelhadas em uma tradicional churrasqueira a carvão a lenha em nossa vila. As asas de frango são marinadas com uma mistura caseira de especiarias, coalhada e um toque de limão para aquele sabor picante perfeito. Assadas lentamente sobre brasas, cada mordida é suculenta, defumada e repleta do autêntico sabor de churrasco.

Veja como assamos as asas até dourarem perfeitamente em espetos, virando-as delicadamente para evitar que queimem e reter a umidade. O aroma defumado, o cozimento natural ao ar livre e as bordas crocantes se unem para fazer desta uma das melhores receitas de frango que já experimentamos.

snippet.title: Doomed in 59 Seconds: Real Stories from the Flight That Never Landed | Ahmedabad Plane Crash
snippet.description:
Doomed in 59 Seconds: Real Stories from the Flight That Never Landed | Ahmedabad Plane Crash
In just 59 seconds, everything changed. What began as a routine flight filled with excited families, first-time flyers, and last-minute goodbye texts, turned into an unthinkable tragedy. As AI 171 took off, some passengers were heading home, others off to summer vacations — none of them knowing it would be their final journey. This video reconstructs the flight moment by moment: from the unusual dip at 14 seconds, to the explosion at 30 seconds. No "landed safely" messages followed. Instead, chaos unfolded on the ground — hospitals overwhelmed, families waiting, lives shattered. Survivors speak: one missed the flight by just hours, another saved by traffic, one more who jumped. This is more than a crash; it’s a story of loss, fate, and the fragile seconds that change everything.
Emergency number 18005691444

snippet.title: Man Escapes Air India Crash by One Flight - He Noticed Something Strange!
snippet.description:
Man Escapes Air India Crash by One Flight - He Noticed Something Strange!


A devastating incident involving Air India Flight 171—a Boeing 787-8 Dreamliner—has resulted in numerous fatalities after the aircraft crashed shortly after takeoff from Ahmedabad airport on its way to London. A passenger who had traveled on the same aircraft just two hours earlier, on a Delhi-to-Ahmedabad leg, took to social media to report troubling technical issues. He pointed out that the air conditioning and in-flight entertainment systems were not functioning, sparking serious concerns about the plane’s upkeep and overall safety.

The tragedy has put a renewed spotlight on Air India’s operational practices, with the passenger’s account raising further doubts about the airline's service standards and safety track record. The Boeing 787-8, equipped with Rolls Royce Trent 1000 engines, has previously encountered mechanical challenges—now prompting investigations into potential system failures or deliberate interference. Indian aviation authorities, in coordination with their British counterparts, are actively probing the cause of the crash amid growing global criticism.

This incident has once again ignited global conversations about the dependability of modern aircraft and the critical need for strict maintenance routines. It also revives scrutiny of Air India’s long-standing reputation, frequently ranked among the least reliable carriers worldwide.

localized.description:
Ahmedabad Plane Crash: खुशबू की रुला देने वाली कहानी ।  Air India | Gujarat News

Ahmedabad Plane Crash: गुजरात के अहमदाबाद में क्रैश हुए एअर इंडिया के विमान AI-171 में अब तक 265 लोगों की मौत की पुष्टि हो चुकी है. इस भीषण विमान हादसे ने पूरे देश को झकझोर कर रख दिया है. इस दुर्घटना में राजस्थान के बालोतरा जिले के अराबा गांव की रहने वाली नई नवेली दुल्हन खुशबू राजपुरोहित की भी मौत हो गई. हादसे से पहले बनी खुशबू की विदाई की एक वीडियो सोशल मीडिया पर खूब वायरल हो रही है। जिसमें पूरा परिवार खुशबू को रोते हुए विदा कर रहा है और वह भी सबके गले लगकर फूट-फूटकर रोती नजर आ रही है।

snippet.title: डबल ईंजन इतनी आसानी से फेल नहीं होता, फिर क्या हुआ?
snippet.description:
AI 171 के साथ साथ अस्पताल के हॉस्टल से भी भयावह ख़बरें आ रही हैं। बड़ी संख्या में मेडिकल छात्र गंभीर रुप से घायल हुए हैं। इनमें कितनों की जान नहीं बच सकी है, इसकी आधिकारिक घोषणा नहीं हुई है। गृहमंत्री अमित शाह ने कहा है कि इस दुर्घटना के पीछे कोई साज़िश नहीं है। यह एक दुर्घटना है। अमित शाह ने घटना स्थल का दौरा किया है और शोक संतप्त परिवारों के साथ खड़े रहने का भरोसा दिलाया है। सोशल मीडिया में ड्रीमलाइनर विमानों के रख-रखाव को लेकर सवाल उठ रहे हैं। आने वाले दिनों में इस सवालों पर बहस और साफ होगी लेकिन हमने आरंभिक स्तर पर इन सवालों को भी शामिल किया है। यह घटना बहुत दुखदायी है। काश हमें इस पर वीडियो नहीं बनाना पड़ता।

snippet.title: Young Air India Crew Member From Manipur Killed in Flight AI171 Crash
snippet.description:
Just hours before boarding Air India Flight AI171 to London, 21-year-old Nganthoi Sharma from Manipur made a final call to her sister. Minutes after takeoff, the aircraft crashed near Ahmedabad, leaving her family in shock and mourning. As DNA identification continues, her loved ones remember a vibrant young woman who followed her dreams into the skies—only to be lost too soon.

#AirIndiaCrash #ManipurMourning #FlightAI171 #AviationTragedy

ja.title: マニプール出身の若いエア・インディア乗務員がAI171便墜落事故で死亡
ja.description:

pt-BR.title: Jovem tripulante da Air India de Manipur morre em acidente com o voo AI171
pt-BR.description:
Poucas horas antes de embarcar no voo AI171 da Air India para Londres, Nganthoi Sharma, de 21 anos, de Manipur, fez uma última ligação para sua irmã. Minutos após a decolagem, a aeronave caiu perto de Ahmedabad, deixando sua família em choque e luto. Enquanto a identificação de DNA continua, seus entes queridos se lembram de uma jovem vibrante que seguiu seus sonhos rumo aos céus — apenas para se perder cedo demais.

#AcidenteAirIndia #LutoManipur #VooAI171 #TragédiaAviação

hi.title: मणिपुर के युवा एयर इंडिया चालक दल के सदस्य की विमान संख्या AI171 दुर्घटना में मौत
hi.description:
लंदन जाने वाली एयर इंडिया की फ्लाइट AI171 में सवार होने से कुछ घंटे पहले मणिपुर की 21 वर्षीय नगंतोई शर्मा ने अपनी बहन को आखिरी कॉल की। ​​उड़ान भरने के कुछ ही मिनटों बाद अहमदाबाद के पास विमान दुर्घटनाग्रस्त हो गया, जिससे उसका परिवार सदमे और शोक में डूब गया। डीएनए पहचान जारी रहने के साथ, उसके प्रियजन एक जीवंत युवा महिला को याद करते हैं, जिसने अपने सपनों का पीछा करते हुए आसमान में उड़ान भरी थी - लेकिन बहुत जल्दी खो गई।

id.title: Awak Muda Air India Asal Manipur Tewas dalam Kecelakaan Pesawat AI171
id.description:
Beberapa jam sebelum menaiki Pesawat Air India AI171 menuju London, Nganthoi Sharma yang berusia 21 tahun dari Manipur menelepon saudara perempuannya untuk terakhir kalinya. Beberapa menit setelah lepas landas, pesawat itu jatuh di dekat Ahmedabad, membuat keluarganya terkejut dan berduka. Saat identifikasi DNA terus berlanjut, orang-orang yang dicintainya mengenang seorang wanita muda yang bersemangat yang mengejar mimpinya ke angkasa—hanya untuk segera meninggal.

#AirIndiaCrash #ManipurMourning #FlightAI171 #AviationTragedy

de-DE.title: Junges Air India-Crewmitglied aus Manipur bei Absturz von Flug AI171 getötet
de-DE.description:
Nur wenige Stunden vor dem Boarding des Air-India-Fluges AI171 nach London rief die 21-jährige Nganthoi Sharma aus Manipur ihre Schwester noch einmal an. Wenige Minuten nach dem Start stürzte das Flugzeug in der Nähe von Ahmedabad ab und ließ ihre Familie in Schock und Trauer zurück. Während die DNA-Identifizierung weitergeht, erinnern sich ihre Angehörigen an eine dynamische junge Frau, die ihren Träumen in den Himmel folgte – nur um viel zu früh verloren zu gehen.

en.title: Young Air India Crew Member From Manipur Killed in Flight AI171 Crash
en.description:

Minutes after takeoff, the aircraft crashed near Ahmedabad, leaving her family in shock and mourning. As DNA identification continues, her loved ones remember a vibrant young woman who followed her dreams into the skies—only to be lost too soon.

id.title: Kecelakaan pesawat Air India: Apa yang Kita Ketahui Sejauh Ini
id.description:
#planecrash #Ahmedabadcrash #airindiaplanecrash

Nama mantan kepala menteri Gujarat, Vijay Rupani, ada dalam daftar penumpang pesawat Air India yang jatuh di dekat Bandara Internasional Ahmedabad pada hari Kamis. Namun, sumber yang dekat dengannya mengatakan kepada TNIE bahwa dia tidak ada di dalam pesawat dan telah mengambil penerbangan yang berbeda.

snippet.title: सुपरमैन (Superman) | New Hindi Trailer
snippet.description:
११ जुलाई से, पूरी दुनिया की नज़रें ऊपर होंगी, देखिये 'सुपरमैन' का नया हिंदी ट्रेलर - Only In Cinemas and IMAX in English, Hindi, Tamil & Telugu. In 3D & IMAX 3D.

Website: www.warnerbros-india.com
Facebook:   / warnerbrosindia  
Instagram:   / warnerbrosindia  
X: https://x.com/WarnerBrosIndia 

“Superman,” DC Studios’ first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who’s driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind. 

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (“Twisters,” “Hollywood”) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (“The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel”) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the “X-Men” movies, “Juror #2”) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (“For All Mankind”), Anthony Carrigan (“Barry,” “Gotham”), Nathan Fillion (the “Guardians of the Galaxy” films, “The Suicide Squad”), Isabela Merced (“Alien Romulus”), Skyler Gisondo (“Licorice Pizza,” “Booksmart”), Sara Sampaio (“At Midnight”), María Gabriela de Faría (“The Moodys”), Wendell Pierce (“Selma,” “Tom Clancy’s Jack Ryan”), Alan Tudyk (“Andor”), Pruitt Taylor Vince (“Bird Box”) and Neva Howell (“Greedy People”).

“Superman” is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (“The Last of Us”) and editors William Hoy (“The Batman”) and Craig Alpert (“Deadpool 2,” “Blue Beetle”).  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, “Superman,” which will be in Cinemas and IMAX® in India on July 11, 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

#WarnerBrosIndia #Superman #SupermanHindiTrailer

snippet.title: ENG vs WI | 3rd T20I | Cricket Highlights | West Indies Tour Of England | 10th June 2025
snippet.description:
England secured a dominant 37-run victory over West Indies in the 3rd T20I at Utilita Bowl, Southampton. Batting first, England posted a massive 248/3 in 20 overs, with Ben Duckett leading the charge with an explosive 84 off 46 balls. West Indies fought hard but fell short, managing 211/8 in their chase. With this win, England completed a 3-0 series sweep, asserting their dominance in the shortest format.

snippet.title: मैंने काशीनाथ के आखों मे कातिया का काल देखा है - Bollywood Action Movie - Sunny Deol - Ghatak
snippet.description:
#b4ufilmy #bollywood #hindi #hindimovie #movie #action #thriller #sunnydeol #meenakshiseshadri

फिल्म का नाम: घातक
कलाकार: सनी देओल, मीनाक्षी शेषाद्रि, अमरीश पुरी और डैनी डेन्जोंगपा
निर्देशक: राजकुमार संतोषी 
म्यूजिक : आर. डी. बर्मन

Movie Name : Ghatak
Cast : Sunny Deol, Meenakshi Seshadri, Amrish Puri, and Danny Denzongpa
Director: Rajkumar Santoshi
Music: R. D. Burman

घातक :- 
काशी नाथ बनारस के रहने वाले दयालु पहलवान और शंभू नाथ के कर्तव्यनिष्ठ दत्तक पुत्र हैं। शंभू नाथ, जो तंबर पत्र से सम्मानित स्वतंत्रता सेनानी थे, शहर में एक सम्मानित और प्रतिष्ठित व्यक्ति हैं। काशी, शंभू के साथ, शंभू के इलाज के लिए मुंबई आता है और अपने भाई शिव नाथ के साथ रहता है। काशी कॉलोनी में गौरी से मिलती है और उसे पसंद करने लगती है। उसे पता चलता है कि कॉलोनी को अत्याचारी गैंगस्टर, कात्या और उसके छह भाइयों द्वारा आतंकित किया जा रहा है। काशी के आगमन से पहले, सचदेव नामक एक निवासी ने कात्या के खिलाफ विद्रोह शुरू करने की कोशिश की, लेकिन उसने उसे बेरहमी से मार डाला, जिससे सचदेव की पत्नी मालती पागल हो गई। कात्या और उसके भाई काशी के दुश्मन बन जाते हैं जब वह मालती के साथ मारपीट करने की प्रक्रिया में उनके गुंडों की पिटाई करता है।

Ghatak :-
Kashi Nath is a kind-hearted wrestler and the dutiful adopted son of Shambhu Nath, living in Banaras. Shambhu Nath, who was a freedom fighter awarded with the Tambra Patra, is an honourable and respectable man in town. Kashi, along with Shambhu, comes to Mumbai for medical treatment for Shambhu and stays with his brother, Shiv Nath. Kashi meets Gauri in the colony and starts liking her. He learns that the colony is being terrorized by the tyrannical gangster, Katya, along with his six brothers. Before Kashi's arrival, a resident named Sachdev tried to initiate a revolt against Katya, but got ruthlessly killed by him, thereby making Malti, Sachdev's wife, go mad. Katya and his brothers become enemies with Kashi when he beats up their goons in the process of roughing up Malti.

Subscribe For More Videos : http://goo.gl/v9HBF9

Jethalal gears up for his upcoming trip to the Himalayas, and the colony members also express interest. At the same time, he carefully explains to Bapuji how to handle the shop while he's away. Will Bapuji manage smoothly?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------

snippet.title: Ed Sheeran - Sapphire (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Listen to 'Sapphire' now: https://es.lnk.to/sapphireID

"Sapphire was the first song I finished for Play that made me know where the album was heading. It's why I finished the recording process in Goa surrounded by some of the best musicians in India. It was an incredible creative process. I shot the music video with Liam Pethick and Nic Minns across my India tour earlier this year, we wanted to showcase the beauty and breadth of the country and its culture. The final jigsaw piece for me was getting @Official_ArijitSingh on the record, but it was a journey to get there and such an amazing day of music and family. Me and him have done a full Punjabi version of the song that will come out in the next few weeks, which has a lot more of him on it. This is the album version of the song, and my favourite song on the album. Hope you guys love it. Sapphire out now" - Ed x

Pre-order 'Play' out September 12: https://es.lnk.to/playID

Subscribe to Ed's channel: http://bit.ly/SubscribeToEdSheeran

Colourist: Jonny Tully @jonnytully
No.8 EP: Ollie Ireland @ollieireland

You’re glowing
You colour and fracture the light
You can’t help but shine
And I know that
You carry the world on your back
But look at you tonight
The lights


Your face
Your eyes
Exploding
Like fireworks
In the sky
Sapphire
Touching on your body while you’re pushing on me
Don’t you end the party
I could do this all week
We’ll be dancing till the morning
Go to bed we won’t sleep
Cham cham chamke sitare wargi
Sapphire
Touching on your body while you’re pushing on me
Don’t you end the party
I could do this all week
We’ll be dancing till the morning
Go to bed we won’t sleep
Cham cham chamke sitare wargi
Look what we found
Karma reached out
Into our hearts and pulled us to our feet now
You know the truth is
We could disappear
Anywhere as long as I got you there
When the sun dies
Till the day shines
When I’m with you
There’s not enough time
You are my spring flower
Watching you bloom, wow
We’re are surrounded but I can only see
The lights

snippet.title: Finding Best Paschim Vihar Food With AI Purav Jha In Delhi | Tere Gully Mein Ep 107 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Be The First To Watch All Videos. Download the CurlyTales App: https://curlytale.page.link/DwNd

In this fun-filled episode of Tere Gully Mein, we meet India's Top Youtuber & the one who cracks us up with hilarious mimicry and crazy characters, it's none other than the OG Youtuber @Puravjha_  

This time we go out on the streets of Delhi's Paschim Vihar and explore some iconic hotspots there. Purav is a total foodie and this episode clearly proves that!  

From Little Chef's juicy rolls and wraps to his all-time comfort ice cream spot, Gianis and the ever-crowded Sandos restaurant which is popular among the locals for its north indian delicacies, this episode is your all-access food guide whenever you're in West Delhi. 

What else? Well, we also play a few fun games to bring out the real, candid side of Purav that included Never Have I Ever, a crazy Mimic challenge and ultimately the one where he gets to describe the fellow youtubers and content creators in one word each. It gets way too real! (Something you wouldn't want to miss!)

From talking about his first career break with Harsh Beniwal. his equation with him today to his lady love and his Bihari dialect, he talks about it very candidly. Purav also talks about his skincare routine (because of his girlfriend :D), his most expensive purchase till date and also shares his feelings on getting trolled.

Watch Purav Jha like never before! This video will make you fall in love with him again and will also make you admire his talent even more.

Tune in and drop your thoughts in the comments below!

snippet.title: 900KM at 200km/h in the Rain on BMW R1250 GSA | Autobahn Madness with Supercars!@CherryVlogsCV
snippet.description:
Brussels to Prague on My BMW R1250 GSA | Autobahn Top Speed Test in the Rain! 🌧🏍💨

Join me on an epic ride from Brussels to Prague, with a scenic detour through Luxembourg and an adrenaline-pumping blast down the German Autobahn — where there’s NO speed limit! 🚀

I push my BMW R1250 GSA to its limits alongside high-speed cars, all while navigating wet, rainy conditions. How fast did the GSA really go? How did it handle in the rain? You'll have to watch the full video to find out!

👉 Subscribe for more real-world motorcycle adventures, travel vlogs, and honest riding experiences across Europe.

📍 Route: Brussels 🇧🇪 → Luxembourg 🇱🇺 → Autobahn 🇩🇪 → Prague 🇨🇿
🏍 Bike: BMW R1250 GSA
🌦 Weather: Rainy & wet — but that didn’t stop us!

📹 Sit back, gear up, and enjoy the ride!

Taarak’s boss invites him home but not just for a casual visit. Troubled by the strange events his guest is facing, he’s thinking of asking Taarak for help. Will Taarak accept his request?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

രണ്ടാനച്ഛന്റെ ചെയ്തികളുടെ ഫലമായി സ്വന്തം ജീവിതം പകരം നൽകിയ പെൺകുട്ടി - മഹാലക്ഷ്മി. പരിമിതികളെ പഴി പറയാതെ ജീവിത പാത ചിരിയോടെ നടന്നു കയറുന്നവൾ. ജീവതത്തിൽ അപ്രതീക്ഷിതമായി തേടിയെത്തിയ ദുരന്തത്തിൽ നിന്നും അതിജീവിച്ച് മഹസക്ഷ്മിയ്ക്ക് കൂട്ടിനെത്തുന്ന കണ്ണൻ. മഹാലക്ഷ്മിയുടേയും കണ്ണൻ്റേയും അതിജീവന കഥ ഇവിടെ ആരംഭിക്കുകയാണ്...

Mahalakshmi | Everyday at 08:30 PM | Flowers TV
എല്ലാ ദിവസവും രാത്രി 08.30 മണിക്ക് ഫ്ളവേഴ്സിൽ
#mahalakshmi #newserial #flowerstv
